​ @tunyki  It was written from scratch in HTML, CSS, Javascript, PHP, and it also uses MySQL databases. Most of the site doesn't use any frameworks (except for the recent channel database update, which uses Bootstrap 5).

I should also mention, this tour is kind of out of date, since the site looks and works completely differently now (and English is the default language, since I realized that there are more people who can speak English than people who can only speak Estonian).
